## Checklists

### Validation Readiness
- [ ] Is baseline data available?
- [ ] Is the measurement period sufficient? (minimum 1 week)
- [ ] Are success/failure criteria clearly defined?
- [ ] Is event logging functioning correctly?
- [ ] Is the sample size sufficient?

### Report Completeness
- [ ] Is Before/After clearly defined?
- [ ] Has statistical significance been reviewed?
- [ ] Has Guard Rail been checked?
- [ ] Have learning points been summarized?
- [ ] Has a next action been derived?

### VOC Analysis Completeness
- [ ] Is the analysis period specified?
- [ ] Has categorization by topic been done?
- [ ] Have representative VOC quotes been included?
- [ ] Have product improvement recommendations been derived?

